<div class="benefits-of-shopping aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12">
      
    
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/etc.clientlibs/bajajmall-site/components/content/common/benefits-of-shopping/clientlib.min.b31db22ef23bffed8cc2232f8323ef63.css" type="text/css">



      
      <div class="otherpage">
            <div id="benefitsContainer">
                  <benefits-of-shopping benefitsofshoppingobj="{&quot;selectfield&quot;:&quot;static&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Benefits of shopping at store&quot;,&quot;titleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;benefitsList&quot;:[{&quot;imageIcon&quot;:&quot;https://cms-assets.bajajfinserv.in/is/image/bajajfinance/Authorised_Dealers-1?scl=1&amp;fmt=png-alpha&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitle&quot;:&quot;Authorised Dealers&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;quesTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;richTextBox&quot;:&quot;<p>Shopping for your favourites has never been easier! With over 43,000 trusted local sellers across India, you have endless choices. Explore more than a million genuine products across various categories on EMI. With so many local options, you can shop conveniently without the need to travel far.</p>\r\n&quot;},{&quot;imageIcon&quot;:&quot;https://cms-assets.bajajfinserv.in/is/image/bajajfinance/100Genuine_Products?scl=1&amp;fmt=png-alpha&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitle&quot;:&quot;100% Geniune products&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;quesTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;richTextBox&quot;:&quot;<p>Bajaj Mall features 100% genuine products offered by our trusted partner stores. From the latest mobile phones and electronics to stylish home appliances, cars, and more — shop from a wide range of top brands on easy EMIs without worrying about heavy upfront costs.</p>\r\n&quot;},{&quot;imageIcon&quot;:&quot;https://cms-assets.bajajfinserv.in/is/image/bajajfinance/Instant_Loan_Approval-2?scl=1&amp;fmt=png-alpha&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitle&quot;:&quot;Instant Loan Approval&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;quesTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;richTextBox&quot;:&quot;<p>You can check your loan eligibility online quickly and easily through Bajaj Finserv’s digital process. Get instant approval in just a few clicks and head to your nearest partner store to make your purchase.</p>\r\n&quot;},{&quot;imageIcon&quot;:&quot;https://cms-assets.bajajfinserv.in/is/image/bajajfinance/Exclusive_Offers-1?scl=1&amp;fmt=png-alpha&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitle&quot;:&quot;Exclusive Offers&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;quesTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;richTextBox&quot;:&quot;<p>Get exciting deals and offers on various products at Bajaj Finserv partner stores. Discover discounts on home appliances, electronics, and lifestyle products throughout the year. Bajaj Finserv also brings exclusive festive season offers, enabling customers to make the most of their purchases with significant savings.</p>\r\n&quot;},{&quot;imageIcon&quot;:&quot;https://cms-assets.bajajfinserv.in/is/image/bajajfinance/ZeroDownPayment-1?scl=1&amp;fmt=png-alpha&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitle&quot;:&quot;Zero Down Payment&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;quesTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;richTextBox&quot;:&quot;<p> Buy select products at Bajaj Finserv partner stores without paying anything upfront. With zero down payment schemes available on eligible products, you can purchase your desired item right away and pay later in easy instalments.</p>\r\n&quot;},{&quot;imageIcon&quot;:&quot;https://cms-assets.bajajfinserv.in/is/image/bajajfinance/WidestEasyEMIPlans-1?scl=1&amp;fmt=png-alpha&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitle&quot;:&quot;Widest Easy EMI Plans&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;quesTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;richTextBox&quot;:&quot;<p>Enjoy budget-friendly shopping with Bajaj Finserv's flexible EMI plans. Choose repayment tenures of up to 60 months and spread your expenses across manageable monthly payments. Whether you're purchasing a home appliance, a mobile phone, or a vehicle, Bajaj Finserv's Easy EMI plans help you shop stress-free.</p>\r\n&quot;},{&quot;imageIcon&quot;:&quot;https://cms-assets.bajajfinserv.in/is/image/bajajfinance/Lowest_EMI_Options-1?scl=1&amp;fmt=png-alpha&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitle&quot;:&quot;Lowest EMI Options&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;quesTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;richTextBox&quot;:&quot;<p>Bajaj Mall offers the lowest EMI options so you can buy mobiles, electronics, furniture, and more by paying easy monthly instalments that fit your budget without any burden.</p>\r\n&quot;},{&quot;imageIcon&quot;:&quot;https://cms-assets.bajajfinserv.in/is/image/bajajfinance/Product_Comparison-1?scl=1&amp;fmt=png-alpha&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitle&quot;:&quot;Product Comparison&quot;,&quot;imageSubTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;quesTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;richTextBox&quot;:&quot;<p>Bajaj Mall allows you to compare multiple products based on specifications, features, and pricing. This comparison helps you evaluate options thoroughly and make an informed decision.</p>\r\n&quot;}],&quot;extractedData&quot;:{}}">
                  </benefits-of-shopping>
            </div>
      </div>

</div>
