        <faq-component faqcomponentobj="{&quot;componentType&quot;:&quot;staticComponentType&quot;,&quot;faqTitle&quot;:&quot;Frequently asked questions&quot;,&quot;showMoreColorText&quot;:&quot;#FF6700&quot;,&quot;faqTitleColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;showLessColorText&quot;:&quot;#FF6700&quot;,&quot;showMore&quot;:&quot;Show More&quot;,&quot;showLess&quot;:&quot;Show Less&quot;,&quot;faqListItems&quot;:[{&quot;question&quot;:&quot;What is Bajaj Mall?&quot;,&quot;faqQuestionTextColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;faqAnswerTextColor&quot;:&quot;#333333&quot;,&quot;answer&quot;:&quot;<p>Bajaj Mall is a digital platform where you can explore electronics, home appliances, gadgets, and more. It provides all the essential product details and guides you to partner stores where you can complete your purchase using a pre-approved loan, repayable through Easy EMIs.</p>\r\n&quot;},{&quot;question&quot;:&quot;How do I know if I am eligible for Easy EMI loan?&quot;,&quot;faqQuestionTextColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;faqAnswerTextColor&quot;:&quot;#333333&quot;,&quot;answer&quot;:&quot;<p>You can check if you are eligible for an Easy EMI loan by verifying if you have a pre-approved loan offer from Bajaj Finserv. If you are pre-approved, you are automatically eligible to shop using Easy EMIs. You can also shop on Easy EMIs with a pre-existing Bajaj Finserv Insta EMI Card.</p>\r\n&quot;},{&quot;question&quot;:&quot;Can I shop with zero down payment?&quot;,&quot;faqQuestionTextColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;faqAnswerTextColor&quot;:&quot;#333333&quot;,&quot;answer&quot;:&quot;<p>Yes, zero down payment is available on select products at Bajaj Finserv partner stores. This means you do not need to pay anything upfront while converting your purchase into Easy EMIs.</p>\r\n&quot;},{&quot;question&quot;:&quot;Are there any ongoing offers on Bajaj Mall?&quot;,&quot;faqQuestionTextColor&quot;:&quot;#1A1A1A&quot;,&quot;faqAnswerTextColor&quot;:&quot;#333333&quot;,&quot;answer&quot;:&quot;<p>Yes, Bajaj Mall frequently updates its offers based on product categories and brands. You can explore the current deals after confirming your profile details.</p>\r\n&quot;}],&quot;faqListBPCFItems&quot;:[]}">
